{"tid":1642202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"弱弱一問，點解依家黨鐵唔駛罰錢？","createTime":"2019-10-09T15:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:00:06.000Z","uid":319784,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3b9ff20164286c0cdfb4aa97a0ba61676fcded","tid":1642202,"uid":319784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>在2016年因有8宗超過31分鐘的延誤而罰款1100萬</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20160106/00407_032.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160106%2F00407_032.html&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5wmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=cadf6a0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20160106/00407_032.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>在2018年就四線故障罰800萬</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/17308/港鐵-港鐵四線故障-信號系統故障-17316/港鐵四線故障罰800萬-車務總監：不知悉兩個信號系統不匹配-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F17308%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%9B%9B%E7%B7%9A%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C-%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C-17316%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%9B%9B%E7%B7%9A%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E7%BD%B0800%E8%90%AC-%E8%BB%8A%E5%8B%99%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D-&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5wmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=50ab267c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/17308/港鐵-港鐵四線故障-信號系統故障-17316/港鐵四線故障罰800萬-車務總監：不知悉兩個信號系統不匹配-</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係點解黨鐵接連2日係8點後提供唔到服務就好似冇話要罰錢？<br />\n<br />\n好啦，可能政府會話因為示威者破壞，所以唔駛罰啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">咁紅磡脫軌個單呢？係黨鐵自己問題啦，點解又唔駛罰？</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190918/s00001/1568775627236/【紅磡出軌】紅磡站有限度服務-乘客-服務尚可接受\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190918%2Fs00001%2F1568775627236%2F%E3%